snippet.title: Mad Miner | Official Early Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Mad Miner coming soon on the Steam!

Mad Miner is a survival and mining game where people are trapped in mines. A miner game where you try to survive in procedurally generated mines.

Website and other links: https://www.mercimekgames.net/
